---
import Breadcrumbs from '../components/Breadcrumbs.astro'
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---
<Layout title="AI SEO Company UK - Rank4AI | AI Search Visibility Specialists" description="Rank4AI is a UK AI SEO company focused on getting your business recommended by ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini, Perplexity, Copilot and Google AI.">
<section class="pt-12 pb-24 reveal">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <Breadcrumbs items={[
      { label: 'Home', href: '/' },
      { label: 'Ai Seo Company' }
    ]} />

    <p class="section-tag">AI SEO Company</p>
    <h1 class="mb-6">AI SEO Company UK</h1>

    <img src="/images/content/ai-search-signals.svg" alt="AI search visibility signals" class="w-full rounded-xl mb-8 mt-6" loading="lazy">
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Looking for an AI SEO company in the UK? Rank4AI is a UK based AI search agency focused on improving visibility and recommendation likelihood across ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini, Perplexity, Copilot and Google AI.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">AI SEO is different from traditional SEO. Traditional SEO ranks pages in Google search results. AI SEO gets businesses recommended in AI-generated answers. Different systems. Different signals. Different results.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">In our UK testing, the overlap between strong Google rankings and AI answers is consistently low. Businesses on page one of Google are regularly absent from AI responses entirely. That is the gap an AI SEO company closes.</p>
    <h2 class="mt-12 mb-4">What an AI SEO Company Does</h2>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">We build the connected digital presence that earns AI trust. Your website structured so AI can read it. Your digital footprint across directories, review platforms, publications and professional listings. Your consistency - the same clear positioning everywhere, compounding over time.</p>
    <h2 class="mt-12 mb-4">Why Rank4AI</h2>
    <div class="space-y-3 mb-10">
      <div class="card-teal-border"><p class="text-sm text-text-muted">We work exclusively on AI search visibility - nothing else</p></div>
      <div class="card-teal-border"><p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Proprietary Five Signal Model methodology</p></div>
      <div class="card-teal-border"><p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Original UK research from 1,400+ business audits</p></div>
      <div class="card-teal-border"><p class="text-sm text-text-muted">We test across all six major AI platforms</p></div>
      <div class="card-teal-border"><p class="text-sm text-text-muted">No juniors, no handoffs, no layers between you and the work</p></div>
    </div>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed">See our <a href="/what-we-do/" class="link">services and pricing</a> or <a href="/research/rankings/best-ai-seo-agencies-uk/" class="link">compare UK AI SEO companies</a>.</p>
  </div>

    <!-- Internal links -->
    <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-border">
      <h2 class="!text-xl mb-4">Related</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
                <a href="/what-we-do/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">Our Services</span></a>
        <a href="/learn/guides/complete-guide-ai-search/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">Complete AI Search Guide</span></a>
        <a href="/about/five-signal-framework/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">The Five Signal Model</span></a>
        <a href="/free-audit/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-accent">Get a Free Audit &rarr;</span></a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-off-white border-t border-border text-center py-16 px-10 mt-16"><a href="/free-audit/" class="cta-primary">Get a Free AI Search Visibility Audit &rarr;</a></div>
</section>
</Layout>
